simulator

Source: R/simulator.R
simulator.Rd

simulator

simulator(grid = 20, Nt = 50, Elim = 5, muG = 0, sigmaG = 1,
  muE = 0, sigmaE = 1, Pfall = 0.01, Rgaps = 2, Pdeath = 0.1,
  Ns = 4, Rdispersal = 1, determinist = TRUE)

Arguments

grid

int. Number of cells per side of the matrix
Nt

int. Number of time steps
Elim

double. Environmental gradient size
muG

double. Mean of genetic values
sigmaG

double. Variance of genetic values
muE

double. Mean of environmental values
sigmaE

double. Variance of environmental values
Pfall

double. Treefall probability
Rgaps

int. Treefall gaps radius
Pdeath

double. Background mortality probability
Ns

int. Number of seedlings per cell
Rdispersal

int. Dispersal radius in cells
determinist

bool. Deterministic or probabilistic vaibility

Value

A data frame.

Examples


simulator()
